comments:
Created 1.4.1990 out of the parishes of Husborne Crawley and Ridgmont. 
    See also Table 2, note (r).

Abolished 1.4.1985 and divided between the parishes of Flitton 
    & Greenfield, Flitwick, Pulloxhill and Westoning.
Created 1.4.1985 out of the parishes of Flitton, Pulloxhill, Flitwick and Silsoe. See also Table 2, note (r).

Created 24.3.1888 out of the parishes of Lower Gravenhurst and 
    Upper Gravenhurst. See also Table 2, note (r).
Abolished 1.4.1984 and added to the parish of Shillington.

Abolished 1.4.1933 and added to the parish of Hulcote & Salford. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).

That part which until 30.9.1897 formed part of the parish of 
    Shillington. See also Table 2, note (b).

Created 1.4.1933 out of the parishes of Salford, Holcot and Aspley 
    Guise. See also Table 2, notes (g), (h), (q), (p) and (r).

That part which until 30.9.1897 formed part of the parish of 
    Shillington. See also Table 2, note (b).
Abolished 24.3.1888 and added to the parish of Gravenhurst.

That part which until 1.4.1933 formed part of the parish of 
    Toddington. See also Table 2, note (f).

That part which until 1.4.1907 formed part of the parish of 
    Shillington. See also Table 2, note (d).

That part which until 30.9.1897 formed part of the parish of 
    Shillington. See also Table 2, note (b).

Abolished 1.4.1933 and added to the parish of Hulcote & Salford. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).

On 30.9.1897 the part in Hertfordshire  
    became parts of the parishes of Holwell, Ickleford and Pirton, so that thereafter 
    Shillington was entirely in Bedfordshire. Renamed 2.6.1977 to become the parish 
    of Shillington & Stondon. See also Table 2, notes (b), (d) and (e).

Created 1.4.1985 from the parish of Higham Gobion and part of 
    the parish of Shillington & Stondon. See also Table 2, note (r).

Created 2.6.1977 by renaming the parish of Shillington. Abolished 
    1.4.1985 and divided between the parishes of Shillington and Stondon.

Created 1.4.1985 from the parish of Upper Stondon and part of 
    the parish of Shillington & Stondon. See also Table 2, notes (m) and 
    (r).
Abolished 24.3.1888 and added to the parish of Gravenhurst.
